mailroom (1.0.3) unstable; urgency=medium

  * search: AI-friendly CLI compat. Soft-redirect of search-variant subcommand
    names (email_search, email-search, search_email, search-email) to 'search'
    with a stderr note. Accept --account/-a both before and after the
    subcommand. Add --query/-q as alias for the positional query.
  * search: fix Gmail default-folder failure. list_folders now skips
    \\Noselect / \\NonExistent entries, so the [Gmail] parent no longer enters
    the folder list. When --folder is omitted, prefer the SPECIAL-USE \\All
    folder (Gmail's [Gmail]/All Mail, Fastmail's Archive, etc.) — one SELECT
    instead of iterating every folder.
  * search: multi-account support. --account/-a accepted multiply;
    --all-accounts/-A searches every configured account. Output is now
    always nested by account name ({"acct": [...]}) — breaking change for
    consumers that previously parsed a flat array. --limit applies per
    account.

 -- Weiwu Zhang <a@colourful.land>  Sat, 25 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000

mailroom (1.0.2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * reply: add attachment support. CLI gains --attach (repeatable), MCP reply
    tool gains attachments parameter. create_reply_mime handles multipart/mixed
    with RFC 2231 encoded filenames for non-ASCII names.

 -- Weiwu Zhang <a@colourful.land>  Sat, 18 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000

mailroom (1.0.1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Rename CLI commands to aerc-aligned short verbs (search, move, reply, etc.)
  * Rename MCP tools to kebab-case (search, move, mark-read, etc.)
  * Add read command to view email content
  * Add folders command to list email folders
  * Normalize all commands to use --folder/-f and --uid/-u named flags
  * Rename import-email to copy (JMAP alignment)
  * Rename process-email to triage, download-attachment to save, etc.

 -- Weiwu Zhang <a@colourful.land>  Mon, 06 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000

